gomodel:SYNGO_3984  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 3b shows that LC3 copurifies with postsynaptic densities. Fig. 3 g-i shows colocalization of LC3 with the postsynaptic protein caldendrin. Microscopy does not allow exact localization to either post- or presynapse.. Experimental description: Hippocampal neuronal cultures from 18 day-old embryonic rats were prepared. p 968" ;
